<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح الإسناد:</span> م <span class="c2">(٤/ ٢٠٩)</span> مختصراً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>